{"title":"Windows 下通过 Scoop 为 VSCode 配置 clangd","uid":"bf8182607cfdb3b14d8fec4dc20a2905","slug":"Windows 下通过 Scoop 为 VSCode 配置 Clangd","date":"2022-05-11T21:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-12-21T22:00:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows 下通过 Scoop 为 VSCode 配置 Clangd.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"准备工作\"><a href=\"#准备工作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"准备工作\"></a>准备工作</h2><p>安装 <a href=\"https://scoop.sh/\">Scoop</a></p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Invoke-WebRequest</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">get.scoop.sh</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> | </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Invoke-Expression</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"安装-Clangd\"><a href=\"#安装-Clangd\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 Clangd\"></a>安装 Clangd</h2><p>安装 <a href=\"https://winlibs.com/\">Winlibs</a> 编译的 MinGW + Clang + clangd</p>\n<div class=\"language-shell\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">shell</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">scoop</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">install</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">mingw-winlibs</span></span></code></pre></div><p>VScode 安装 <a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=llvm-vs-code-extensions.vscode-clangd\">clangd</a> 扩展。</p>\n<h2 id=\"为什么通过-Scoop-安装？\"><a href=\"#为什么通过-Scoop-安装？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"为什么通过 Scoop 安装？\"></a>为什么通过 Scoop 安装？</h2><p>通过 Scoop 安装 clangd 可以自动配置环境变量，而且还可以避免 VSCode 找不到 <code>#include</code>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考资料\"><a href=\"#参考资料\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考资料\"></a>参考资料</h2><ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/508819503\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/508819503</a></li>\n</ol>\n","text":"准备工作安装 Scoop shellInvoke-WebRequest get.scoop.sh | Invoke-Expression安装 Clangd安装 ...","permalink":"/post/Windows 下通过 Scoop 为 VSCode 配置 Clangd","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":287,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"编程","slug":"编程","count":1,"path":"api/categories/编程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vscode","slug":"Vscode","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Vscode.json"},{"name":"Windows","slug":"Windows","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Windows.json"},{"name":"Scoop","slug":"Scoop","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Scoop.json"},{"name":"Clangd","slug":"Clangd","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Clangd.json"},{"name":"gcc","slug":"gcc","count":1,"path":"api/tags/gcc.json"},{"name":"LLVM","slug":"LLVM","count":1,"path":"api/tags/LLVM.json"},{"name":"Clang","slug":"Clang","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Clang.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">准备工作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-Clangd\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装 Clangd</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87-Scoop-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">为什么通过 Scoop 安装？</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">参考资料</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Jiahao","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://imgur.com/a/fLS8gIP","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/TheJiahao","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{}}